CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 7, 1959, pg. 22, reads: "Fifth Bucket - Gary Kenley, Fifth Avenue sharpshooter, finds room in Peabody defense and scores during the exciting playoff game at the South Side Market House Tuesday. Kenley, a junior, left Fifth in scoring with 17 points during the thrilling game, won by Peabody, 65 - 61. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Basketball game with Fifth Avenue High School, including players #32 and #34, against Peabody High School, in South Side Market House
